</div>
</div>

<div class="product-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-name="backpack">
<img src="https://cdn.cosmos.so/7d633d1d-8698-497b-b984-8c0765c74057?format=jpeg" alt="Backpack">
<div class="product-info">
<h4>Laptops</h4>
<div class="rating">★★★★★</div>
